         <div>
            <entry xml:id="Lb8b18a233ab94060b974dd816fb79b4d" n="12843">
               <form><foreign xml:lang="gez">ፓድረ</foreign></form>
               <sense xml:id="Tmain" xml:lang="en" source="#traces"><cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez">
                     <quote>pādra</quote>
                  </cit>, <lbl expand="pluralis">Pl.</lbl>
                  <foreign xml:lang="gez">ፓድሮች፡</foreign>
                  <cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez">
                     <quote>pādročč</quote>
                  </cit>
                  <cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                     <quote>Jesuit</quote>
                  </cit>, member of the Society of Jesus <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወኮነ፡ ምክንያተ፡ ስደቶሙ፡
                     ለመሃይምናን፡ ሶበ፡ መጽኡ፡ ቦሙ፡ አልባሰ፡ አባግዕ፡ ተኵላት፡ ወሣጥያን፡ ወአክይስት፡ ቀታልያን፡ ዘውእቶሙ፡ ፓድሮች፡
                     አርድእተ፡ ልዮን፡ ስሑት፡ መዝገበ፡ ዕልወት፡ ወዓመፃ።</foreign> ‘<cit type="translation" xml:lang="fr">
                     <quote>La raison de l’expulsion des croyants fut qu’il arriva contre eux, sous
                        l’aspect de brebis, des loups déchireurs et des serpents meurtriers, qui
                        étaient les pādroč, les disciples de Léon, le séducteur, le réceptacle du
                        crime et de la perfidie.</quote>
                  </cit>’ <bibl><ptr target="bm:ContiRossini1909LiberT"/><citedRange unit="page"> 76
                        l. 27–29 (ed.)</citedRange></bibl>, <bibl><ptr target="bm:ContiRossini1910LiberV"/><citedRange unit="page"> 92 l. 10–13
                        (tr.)</citedRange></bibl>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወኮነ፡ ምክንያተ፡ ስደቶሙ፡ ለምእመናን፡
                     ሶበ፡ አምጽኡ፡ ቦሙ፡ ፓድሮች፡ ሃይማኖተ፡ ልዮን፡ ቈላፍ፡ ምልዕተ፡ ዓመፃ፡ ወርኵስ።</foreign> ‘<cit type="translation" xml:lang="fr">
                     <quote>L’occasion de la persécution des croyants fut que les pādroč
                        apportèrent, contre eux, la foi de Léon l’incirconcis, pleine de fraude et
                        d’impureté. </quote>
                  </cit>’ <bibl><ptr target="bm:ContiRossini1909LiberT"/><citedRange unit="page"> 78
                        l. 3–5 (ed.)</citedRange></bibl>, <bibl><ptr target="bm:ContiRossini1910LiberV"/><citedRange unit="page"> 94 l. 6–8
                        (tr.)</citedRange></bibl>
                  <sense n="E" xml:id="TE">from Amharic, from Spanish ‘padre’ <cit type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                        <quote>father</quote>
                     </cit>
                  </sense>
                  <nd/>
               </sense>
